### 5d. Add to Railway
In Railway Variables, add:
```
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY = sk_test_your_key
STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY = pk_test_your_key
STRIPE_PRO_PRICE_ID = price_your_pro_id
STRIPE_BUSINESS_PRICE_ID = price_your_business_id
```

