## ğŸ†˜ Help!

**If something doesn't work:**

1. Check Railway logs (Deployments â†’ View Logs)
2. Check browser console (F12)
3. Verify environment variables are set
4. Make sure all files uploaded correctly

**Common Issues:**

- "Page not found" â†’ Files didn't upload correctly
- "Login doesn't work" â†’ Check environment variables
- "Can't create links" â†’ Check database permissions

